<br>
Crow and I made a raid into the montain halls tonight. Our first pass was not a success. I must point out that I took Crow, as he was logging in, unprepared. I told him that, if he would like to come with me in the halls, he had to come right away. I had only one hour ahead of me. (in the past, I did the same with Haggriden and Celeroy. I guess it must be very annoying for you guys.)<br>
<br>
In this first pass, I was killed. Then Crow took the time to restock and we went back. <br>
<br>
Have you ever noticed that Crow was at his best on a rescue mission?<br>
<br>
The fight was terrific! I had to drink 3 stam elexir to keep up with it! (for an archer, thats not usual) About 25 drudges non stop. (More or less??? Crow? How many did you count?)<br>
<br>
It's been a long time since the old terrying duo had dominated a dungeon like this, and it was good!<br>
<br>
Thanks Crow for tonight's hunt! <br>
<br>
I hope that others will come there too, we still have guts to find. (on the raveners and in ourself!)<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
